        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nVijay is at the F2F and sent these comments:\n\nthis jira ticket https://jira.onap.org/browse/DCAEGEN2-1129   \nalso identifies new relationtype - clamp_node.relationships.gets_input_from to be defined, which i don't see on the current type file\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/dcaegen2/platform/plugins/tree/relationships/relationship-types.yaml   \nsimilar relationship type should be added.. i guess it can be added into same nodetype file",
